<li id="cite_note-110"><b><a href="#cite_ref-110" title="">^</a></b> Annette Gordon-Reed, <i>Thomas Jefferson and Sally Hemings: An American Controversy</i>, Charlottesville: University of Virginia Press, 1997, p.209</li>
