<li id="cite_note-112"><b><a href="#cite_ref-112" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/jefferson/cron/1902sprig.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/jefferson/cron/1902sprig.html" rel="nofollow">"A Sprig of Jefferson was Eston Hemings"</a>. <i>Jefferson's Blood</i>. Public Broadcasting Service<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/jefferson/cron/1902sprig.html" class="external free" title="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/jefferson/cron/1902sprig.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/jefferson/cron/1902sprig.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-04-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=A+Sprig+of+Jefferson+was+Eston+Hemings&amp;rft.atitle=Jefferson%27s+Blood&amp;rft.pub=Public+Broadcasting+Service&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Fwgbh%2Fpages%2Ffrontline%2Fshows%2Fjefferson%2Fcron%2F1902sprig.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Thomas_Jefferson"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
