ity of Virginia School of Medicine">School of Medicine</a> (SMD)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/University_of_Virginia_School_of_Nursing" title="University of Virginia School of Nursing">School of Nursing</a> (NURS/GNUR)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Judge_Advocate_General%27s_Corps,_U.S._Army" title="Judge Advocate General's Corps, U.S. Army" class="mw-redirect">US Army Judge Advocate General’s School</a><br />
