<b>Current Facilities:</b> Aquatics and Fitness Center<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> Birdwood Golf Course<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Davenport_Field" title="Davenport Field">Davenport Field</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/John_Paul_Jones_Arena" title="John Paul Jones Arena">John Paul Jones Arena</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kl%C3%B6ckner_Stadium" title="Klöckner Stadium">Klöckner Stadium</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Lake_Monticello,_Virginia" title="Lake Monticello, Virginia">Lake Monticello</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> Lannigan Track<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Memorial_Gymnasium_(Virginia)" title="Memorial Gymnasium (Virginia)">Memorial Gym</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> Panorama Farms<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> The Park<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Scott_Stadium" title="Scott Stadium">Scott Stadium</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sheridan_Snyder_Tennis_Center" title="Sheridan Snyder Tennis Center">Sheridan Snyder Tennis Center</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> Turf Field<br />
